{"tid":1052971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔見銀包","createTime":"2019-03-08T16:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T15:16:38.000Z","uid":35488,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7933924ec31dfdf8f77ddda5793f237e125060e9","tid":1052971,"uid":35488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T16:18:31.000Z","msg":"今日夜晚九點到係九龍塘站落車 (我係將軍澳上車)<br />\n臨出閘先發現唔見啡色皮銀包<br />\n問過客戶服務中心都冇執到<br />\n入面有少量現金、身份證學生八達通同城大學生證<br />\n個銀包係我女朋友親手整比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上面刻左我個名<br />\n我好中意個銀包<br />\n如果有好心人執到希望你高抬貴手交比警署/MTR<br />\n個銀包對我真係好重要<br />\n唔該哂大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/khc1997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkhc1997&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=e90d9678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/khc1997</a>"},{"pid":"1e8c0e8ec20e6cb5439ea5b89c9bbbd25171d199","tid":1052971,"uid":35488,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T16:38:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28354c4c567568927247cbf29c7322a7f89b142f","tid":1052971,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T16:39:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f87458b4923b4ddaf8d48a33d1e701085098f9b8","tid":1052971,"uid":233267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T16:52:47.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"43ce07ba9ffd13a421e37afda493a55f8eb93c1e","tid":1052971,"uid":35488,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T17:11:41.000Z","msg":"多謝兩位巴打幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4393e44a1a843d3d849a70d5b7020e48ca12ce7f","tid":1052971,"uid":85805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T17:16:18.000Z","msg":"好似有人係紅磡執到 執左粉嶺<br />\n等我搵搵先"},{"pid":"2c3b2252e63edec9ee48679dbc97038293ec03cf","tid":1052971,"uid":85805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"This one?"},{"pid":"10e5c50b936449cea55d5e824679a24b5b49ec52","tid":1052971,"uid":85805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T17:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/09/012222_39ca249ff5d433e4b4e9ddf068b65d81.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F09%2F012222_39ca249ff5d433e4b4e9ddf068b65d81.png&h=4b271074&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50fc0f58cf3c10353086d60054bf7b1c061f02a5","tid":1052971,"uid":35488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"10e5c50b936449cea55d5e824679a24b5b49ec52","tid":1052971,"uid":85805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T17:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/09/012222_39ca249ff5d433e4b4e9ddf068b65d81.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F09%2F012222_39ca249ff5d433e4b4e9ddf068b65d81.png&h=4b271074&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"巴打有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係呢個唔係我架<br />\n我個個再淺色啲"},{"pid":"a11c0e97d4b9f88b5b256d2a5eaf0de127d9514d","tid":1052971,"uid":35488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T18:15:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"411a9495d381297ed54845b3a707dc1aad3a23bd","tid":1052971,"uid":4686,"like":0,"disli